  "Admiralty" = "WOODLANDS",
  "Ang Mo Kio" = "ANG MO KIO",
  "Boon Lay (East)" = "BOON LAY",
  "Changi" = "CHANGI",
  "Choa Chu Kang (South)" = "CHOA CHU KANG",
  "Clementi" = "CLEMENTI",
  "East Coast Parkway" = "BEDOK",

weather <- weather[, c("Subzone", setdiff(names(weather), "Subzone"))]
